    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/27ddc8b443cdc01b86a60f1b999f7953.poster.avif?t=1695116176\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/27ddc8b443cdc01b86a60f1b999f7953.webm?t=1695116176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/27ddc8b443cdc01b86a60f1b999f7953.mp4?t=1695116176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome Home is a murder mystery set in two timelines in which you play both the murderer in the past and the investigator in the future. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/a243678c8ad03528b5dd0a0824bc82f2.avif?t=1695116176\" width=600 height=320 /></span><br>Play as a murderer in 1922, infiltrating a family house, solving puzzles and discovering the unspoken secrets of the Moore family.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/460d27fdef4f02ac136129561a7f508e.avif?t=1695116176\" width=600 height=320 /></span><br>Play as a tourist in 1987 exploring the house now turned museum, investigating it, gathering clues and piecing together the events of that horrific night.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/94780b2c9134f934acf5080988734221.avif?t=1695116176\" width=600 height=320 /></span><br>Can you uncover the decades old dark truth haunting your family?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1696450/extras/da1129d80aa1fec292a526485892b3e4.avif?t=16